  </div>
</div><div class="row margin-bottom-10">
  <div class="col-md-12">
    <p>So we made our way back to the campsite. We enjoyed a nice dinner, but unfortunately, there was another thunderstorm nearby this evening. We decided to go to bed and hope for better weather tomorrow. Tomorrow we'll slowly start heading south through Sydney.</p>
